snippet.textDisplay:
Tati, big fan of yours here from Iceland. 🤗😘
Everything here is so over priced so I do order alot online. Because most of the time, even with the sending cost and the toll/custom, is cheaper then to buy it here...
Where would you recommend me to buy, for exeemple, those ELF products that send to my country?
Of course I have ordered your pallet and the Blendiful. And i ordered three of those. One to give away and then two for myself. Just waiting for it to arrave. More then a month since i orderd it. 🙃
I'm an beauty-products-addict.. and im not just calling me that. Its almost like a sirious thing that people have had worried about 😊🤦🏻‍♀️🤓 but hey, thats just my thing. I just hide new purchases. 😎🤐🤫😉
I haven't received your products tho, coz everytime i order online it takes FOREVER to finally arrive here to my small and cold island.
But anyway, i try to watch all of your videos and i just Looouuuuveee your passion and honesty 😘
I do have one recuest tho... i would like to see you try the magnet eyeliner and eyelashes. Would love to hear your take on that. Ive seen many people try it in videos but obviously I would listen and trust your opinion more then other once. I also kinda wanna ask you for an advice about how to start getting myself out there and start working as a make-up artist. I mean, i have a diploma from many years ago but i do not belive that im good enough and that stops me, not just in make-up but in life to. But thats another story 🧐😉😁
Anyways.... this wasn't supposed to be this long.
I dont even know if you'll see this or read this but i just have to try to reach out.
I really hope you see this. But i must admit, I would probably be starstrucked if you would answar and I'd tell everyone i know 🤣🤣
Your sinsire fan and an admirer:
Saerun Heidi Saevarsdottir 😘💋❤👩‍🎨
P.s. A good advice that i got from my teachers is to keep things like eyeliners, paint pot and those tipes of things, upside down when im not using it. Helps the item staying moist and prevent them to dry out and therefore lasts longer 😉👍
